    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new adventure! It\u2019s been super reliable and well-taken care of, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you today. It runs great and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin, I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical health is excellent, highlighted by a comprehensive VANOS service and a professionally reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural integrity. The drivetrain benefits from a factory variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing sharp turn-in and minimizing body roll. With its individual throttle bodies synchronized for crisp response and a linear power band that pulls strongly to the 8,000 RPM redline, this M3 offers a pure, analog performance experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2018 Sedan. Good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Minor cosmetic wear. Interior well-kept.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
